description:
This cloak provides resistance magical damage. The wearer can choose the damage type when attuning.

Currently the cape bears this resistance:
{{resistance}}

This ring grants the wearer advantage on saving throws against fiends and better insight into finding them, additionally granting {{Advantage}} when performing the following skill checks against fiends:
+ {{Investigation}}
+ {{Survival}}
+ {{Insight}}.

A powerful staff that grants the wielder control over magic. Charges may be used to cast these spells:
+ 1 Charge: {{#spell:shield}}
+ 2 Charge: {{#spell:scorchingray}}
+ 3 Charge: {{#spell:fireball}}
